events.name: ファストトラベル移動場所
ファストトラベル移動場所
ファストトラベル移動場所

parameters:
Fotizona Guard: You cannot have an audience without
permission.

Prince Rex: You all made a bad bet! You are inferior to
Caron in terms of military strength, wealth, and power... in
all aspects.
Prince Rex: You all bet against me!
Prince Rex: However... behold this azure sky!

Prince Rex: When the storm subsides, everything will be in
my hands! You heroes! The gold and silver treasures stored
in the royal palace!
Prince Rex: And... the throne awaits the rightful one!

Prince Rex: The wicked Caron will disappear, and the old era
will come to an end. From now on, together with all of you,
we will build a new era!

Prince Rex: I will always be a king who goes to the
battlefield! That is the true form of the rightful king of
the Fotizona Empire!

Prince Rex: Under the reign of the rightful king, the empire
will regain justice and order.

Prince Rex: Raise the flag! Raise the sword! Raise the
spear!
Prince Rex: Gentlemen, this is our complete victory!

Imperial soldiers of the Prince's faction: Long live King
Rex! Long live the rightful king! Long live our new king!
The guarantor of the new era! The hero who slays the wicked
queen!

Imperial soldiers of the Prince's faction: King Rex! Hooray!
The rightful king! Hooray! The true king of the throne, the
hero king of the Fotizona Empire! The hero who slays
dragons!

Prince Rex: Among those who contributed to this victory, the
adventurers from the Futeira Guild stood out.

Prince Rex: The wicked Caron planned to create dragons and
rule the entire empire through fear.
Prince Rex: They are the heroes who stopped that.

Prince Rex: The name of the Dragon Slayers who saved the
empire from dragons not once, but twice, will be forever
engraved in the history of the empire!

Prince Rex: Praise the saviors of the empire! Praise the
heroes of the empire!

Imperial soldiers of the Prince's faction: Praise the heroes
who defeated the dragons! Hooray for the Dragon Slayers!
Hooray for the Futeira Adventurers Guild!

Imperial soldiers of the Prince's faction: The true heroes
who saved the empire twice! Hooray for the Dragon Slayers!
Hooray for the Futeira Adventurers Guild!
Clea: Somehow, it's embarrassing, isn't it?

Mage Relm: Hehe! In times like this, you just need to stand
tall and confident!
Thief Nora: Now that I'm relieved, I'm getting hungry...

Priestess Sophia: It would be nice if they let us go soon...
but it seems unlikely.
Clea: Once we're done here, let's all have a meal together.
Clea: After this, let's move on to the next--
Clea (I see, with this our journey...)
Clea: Let's go back to our everyday lives.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
